Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: PAM module to look for leaked passwords
 This module will test user-submitted passwords against the API
 provided by haveibeenpwnd.com
 .
 This is useful for improving password-policies.
